        <mxCell id="note1" value="&lt;b&gt;Entity Relationships&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• code.user_id → users.id (One-to-One)&lt;br&gt;• refresh_token.user_id → users.id (One-to-Many)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Constraints&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;• users.username is UNIQUE&lt;br&gt;• users.email is UNIQUE&lt;br&gt;• refresh_token.token is UNIQUE&lt;br&gt;• Each code belongs to exactly one user&lt;br&gt;• Each user can have multiple refresh tokens" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;fontSize=11;size=15;" vertex="1" parent="1">
